<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. I Pathien hehpihna thuk zie,
 Zahngaih na in a dim hi;
 Buoina tincheng ei dawn zangkhai,
 Ei vangsak zing zing sek hi.

[V2]
 Hehpih Pathien ahi a (2)

[V3]
 2. Thil a hungum, a beikit sek,
 Mihing a bei kumte le;
 A hehpihna vang a ngei zing,
 Kumsawt a lamdang ngeilo.

[V4]
 3. Eihaw'n vangsietna a I ngaih uh,
 A hehpihna latsak tu;
 Mahleh, thapha'n, lungkham buoina,
 Kipahna'n a siem zaw tai.</lyrics>
<title>GOD IS LOVE</title>
<author>Rev. F.W. Savidge</author>
<hymn_number>430</hymn_number>
</song>